{"tid":2352712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"具惠善提及結婚計畫　「下次一定要辦婚禮！」","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T09:16:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09d2928ac2c95cbe92b8fefcbfd9c736a13c13df","tid":2352712,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_38dcf785fa6b2510fe202c90bcea2500/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-04/132760-891768.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_38dcf785fa6b2510fe202c90bcea2500%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-04%2F132760-891768.png&h=0abe7e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n走過離婚風波的具惠善最近在 KakaoTV 節目上分享個人生活和各種想法，在最新公開的內容中，她還提起了未來舉行婚禮的計畫！<br />\n<br />\nKakaoTV 原創綜藝節目《Face ID》今天（4 日）播出了具惠善系列的最新內容，具惠善和以前念書時的同學見面，兩人聊著聊著便聊到結婚話題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f080f0ad4c68347781b3b4cc2a4dd2d6/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-04/132760-891767.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f080f0ad4c68347781b3b4cc2a4dd2d6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-04%2F132760-891767.png&h=a11fd3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n具惠善說：「我最近正在寫想邀來參加婚禮的名單。因為我沒辦過婚禮，下次一定要辦婚禮。」她透露：「我真的好想好想邀我喜歡的人們來參加，我已經整理好一些了，結果比我想像得還多，有超過十個人。」具惠善於 2016 年和安宰賢結婚時，選擇在夫婦節當天以行善取代婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，具惠善最近活躍在不少網路及電視節目上，同時也在自己的 YouTube 頻道上分享為鋼琴專輯收錄曲所製作的影片，展現多才多藝的面貌。"},{"pid":"114b3cb99493c38bc78d4f2beb1ffcd68bc8c43c","tid":2352712,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"衰女人..."},{"pid":"d49cb6b2b98836b84b867c22ec9cb3d37f03edb1","tid":2352712,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"依個係咪岩岩離婚"},{"pid":"7e99fd7de74c64e4a05254827893b10ab1415055","tid":2352712,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"114b3cb99493c38bc78d4f2beb1ffcd68bc8c43c","tid":2352712,"uid":9309